  "body": "## Summary\n- **NFC task cards** now support \"Start when scanned\" mode for instant self-assignment and automatic status updates, or create unassigned tasks for later pickup\n- **Enhanced NFC programming** with task descriptions, workspace indicators in templates, and confirmation previews showing the exact URL being written to the tag\n- **Improved deep link reliability** across environments with support for new share domains and smarter handling of tenant-specific NFC tap workflows\n- **Instant task access** when tapping NFC tags—automatically navigates to the newly created task detail screen upon completion\n\n## Changes\n\n### NFC & Task Management\n- **Auto-start tasks**: Enable \"Start when scanned\" on NFC task cards to automatically assign the task to whoever scans the tag and move it to \"working\" status; disable to create unassigned tasks\n- **Richer task data**: Add task descriptions when programming NFC tags and view associated workspaces directly in the template dropdown\n- **Simplified creation**: Create NFC tags directly from task templates without manual workspace selection\n- **Confirmation preview**: Programming NFC cards now displays a confirmation modal with the exact URL to be written instead of a generic alert\n- **Updated terminology**: Action labels clarified to \"Create task\" and \"Existing task action\" for better usability\n\n### Deep Links & Authentication\n- **Expanded domain support**: NFC tap workflows now function across `cvx-share.whagons.com`, `cvx-share-dev.whagons.com`, and wildcard subdomains for tenant-specific environments\n- **Flexible URL handling**: Improved support for `uuid` query parameters and tolerant path matching (`/nfc/tap` vs `/nfc/tap/`)\n- **Reliable tenant switching**: Enhanced authentication flow prevents unexpected login redirects when accessing NFC screens and properly manages tenant context from deep links\n- **Pending approval states**: Added support for \"pending approval\" feedback when tapping tags requiring review before completion\n\n## Technical Notes\n- **Support diagnostics**: Integrated mobile support diagnostics with breadcrumb trails (max 40 entries, PII-scrubbed), error correlation IDs, and 30-second heartbeat session tracking for improved debugging of field issues\n- **Build integrity**: Release process now verifies the local `main` branch is synchronized with remote before building to prevent releases from stale or detached states\n- **Windows development**: Added `scripts/run-android-short-path.js` to work around Windows MAX_PATH limitations by executing Android builds from short junction paths\n- **NFC URL format**: Migrated from path-based (`/nfc/tap/{uuid}`) to query-parameter-based (`/nfc/tap?uuid={uuid}&tenantId={tenant}`) URLs for improved routing flexibility\n- **Build**: Version 5.1.22 (Build 38)",
